{"tid":2074602,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"公投-定義「街工」及「梁耀忠」為非民主派","createTime":"2020-06-22T08:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T12:53:12.000Z","uid":39092,"like":4,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1234341061fd4be8ad7f0d180cdc5c46313be44b","tid":2074602,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"都過左幾日<br />\n街工班撚樣都唔出黎道歉<br />\n<br />\n白頭佬你本身已經係香港既千古罪人之一<br />\n就係你搞到出左件大口狗<br />\n今次又帶頭搞9初選<br />\n就算係唔係鬼<br />\n都係毫無政治智慧既垃圾 你無資格無能力再做代議士<br />\n你當日講撚完句「臭罌出臭草」之外就食老本食到25年後既今日<br />\n咩都食夠啦 25年樓都夠供完啦<br />\n<br />\n你做緊既野同馮檢基又有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無功都有勞，比次機會佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「街工」及「梁耀忠」為非民主派"},{"pid":"daa35bdcc0f23f2daf09ec033c0e8a38b6559b4f","tid":2074602,"uid":61511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"不如我呢個REPLY VOTE埋OMDB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2281c0999dfe28c5d2a616e9f6da7ae3d935ea","tid":2074602,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"daa35bdcc0f23f2daf09ec033c0e8a38b6559b4f","tid":2074602,"uid":61511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"不如我呢個REPLY VOTE埋OMDB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:27:26.000Z","msg":"你自己開第2個post la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p